data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of the highly coveted North Port Estates! This 4-bedroom, 2-bath beauty, built in 2019, is a showcase of modern elegance and thoughtful design.  Nestled on a corner lot, surrounded by newer homes, this residence boasts a split floor plan that maximizes space and functionality. As you step through the foyer, envision the possibilities – a dining room, a den, a study, or your own personal media haven. The heart of the home is the expansive great room, seamlessly connected to the gourmet kitchen. Revel in the culinary delights with solid wood cabinets, stainless steel appliances, breakfast bar, eat-in kitchen, and 16 X 16 porcelain tile flooring. Experience the convenience of a Reverse Osmosis system, ensuring crystal-clear water for all your needs. Zebra blinds controlled by remote adorn most windows, allowing you to effortlessly control the natural light that fills the home. Retreat to the ensuite master bath, a spa-like sanctuary featuring a large shower with a seat, a garden tub, dual sinks, and a private water closet – the epitome of luxury.  Step outside to your private oasis – an in-ground, heated saltwater pool with a tranquil waterfall feature. The lanai offers a picturesque view of the pool, which is surrounded by colorful travertine tile and a pool cage. Imagine entertaining or simply relaxing in this idyllic setting. Security is a top priority with an alarm system and four exterior cameras ensuring your peace of mind. For tech-savvy buyers, the Night Owl DVR system is ready for seamless integration. Want to expand your haven? The vacant lot directly behind the home on Spisak Ave is available for an additional $20,000. Create your private greenbelt, set up a workshop, or build a guesthouse – the options are limitless. Explore the potential with MLS# D6134438.     Some photos are virtually staged to ignite your imagination, with actual photos following. Don't miss the chance to make this house your forever home. Contact us today to schedule a tour and turn your dreams into reality!
